kind: llman.sdd.spec
name: "sdd-specs-compaction-guidance"
purpose: "TBD - created by archiving change upgrade-sdd-archive-freeze-and-structured-prompts. Update Purpose after archive."
valid_scope[2]: src/,tests/
valid_commands[1]: "llman sdd validate sdd-specs-compaction-guidance --type spec --strict --no-interactive"
evidence[1]: migrated from openspec
requirements[4]{req_id,title,statement}:
  r1,SDD Specs 压缩治理技能,"`llman sdd update-skills` MUST 生成 `llman-sdd-specs-compact` 技能，提供 specs 压缩治理流程。 该技能 MUST 覆盖： - 现有 specs 盘点与重叠识别 - MUST/Scenario 冗余压缩策略 - 保留主干、迁移附录、归档建议 - 在 archive 历史噪声较大时先执行 freeze 建议（`llman sdd archive freeze --dry-run` 与执行命令） - 压缩后验证步骤与回归命令"
  r2,CLI 入口预留（本次不实现）,SDD 规范 MUST 预留未来 `llman sdd specs compact` CLI 能力，但本次变更 MUST NOT 实现该命令。
  r3,Compaction Guidance Must Reference ISON Source of Truth,Compaction guidance in new style MUST define ISON source artifacts as canonical for compaction decisions.
  r4,Compaction Guidance Includes Safety Regression Check,Compaction guidance MUST include a safety regression comparison step between baseline and compacted outputs.
scenarios[5]{req_id,id,given,when,then}:
  r1,"specs-compact-技能可生成","","用户执行 `llman sdd update-skills --no-interactive --all`","Claude/Codex 目标路径均生成 `llman-sdd-specs-compact/SKILL.md`"
  r1,"specs-compact-包含-freeze-建议","","用户查看生成的 `llman-sdd-specs-compact/SKILL.md`","文本明确建议在 archive 历史较大时先执行 `llman sdd archive freeze --dry-run`"
  r2,"当前版本不暴露-specs-compact-子命令","","用户执行 `llman sdd --help`",帮助中不出现 `specs compact` 子命令
  r3,"compaction-flow-references-canonical-ison-source","",a user follows specs compaction guidance in new style,keep/merge/remove decisions are derived from ISON source artifacts
  r4,"compaction-includes-safety-check-gate","",a compaction plan is prepared,the workflow includes a before/after safety check gate
